    <title>个性化shell终端折腾</title>
    <link href="https://yzllee.github.io/blog/2017/08/04/shell/"/>
    <id>https://yzllee.github.io/blog/2017/08/04/shell/</id>
    <published>2017-08-04T08:05:32.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-08-04T10:20:07.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在MAC环境下自定义shell终端的配色方案。<br>iterm2 + oh my zsh</p>
<a id="more"></a>
<h2 id="安装iterm2"><a href="#安装iterm2" class="headerlink" title="安装iterm2"></a>安装iterm2</h2><p><a href="http://www.iterm2.com/downloads.html" target="_blank" rel="external">下载地址</a></p>
<h2 id="安装oh-my-zsh"><a href="#安装oh-my-zsh" class="headerlink" title="安装oh-my-zsh"></a>安装oh-my-zsh</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">curl -L https://raw.github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/master/tools/install.sh | sh</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>安装完成后，切换<code>dash</code>:<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">chsh -s /bin/zsh</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>切换为原来的<code>dash</code>:<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">chsh -s /bin/bash</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>卸载oh-my-zsh:<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">uninstall_oh_my_zsh</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="设置配色方案"><a href="#设置配色方案" class="headerlink" title="设置配色方案"></a>设置配色方案</h2><p>使用 <a href="http://ethanschoonover.com/solarized" target="_blank" rel="external">Solarized</a> 配色方案:<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment">#下载</span></div><div class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> git://github.com/altercation/solarized.git</div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#配置</span></div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> solarized</div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> vim-colors-solarized/colors</div><div class="line">mkdir -p ~/.vim/colors</div><div class="line">cp solarized.vim ~/.vim/colors/</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#更改vim配色方案，和终端保持一致</span></div><div class="line">vi ~/.vimrc</div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#写入</span></div><div class="line">syntax <span class="built_in">enable</span></div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span> background=dark</div><div class="line">colorscheme solarized</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#配置ls高亮</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#安装coreutils</span></div><div class="line">brew install coreutils</div><div class="line">vi ~/.bash_profile</div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#写入</span></div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> CLICOLOR=1</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="设置语法高亮"><a href="#设置语法高亮" class="headerlink" title="设置语法高亮"></a>设置语法高亮</h2><p>使用 <a href="https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting" target="_blank" rel="external">zsh-syntax-highlighting</a><br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting.git</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"source <span class="variable">$&#123;(q-)PWD&#125;</span>/zsh-syntax-highlighting/zsh-syntax-highlighting.zsh"</span> &gt;&gt; <span class="variable">$&#123;ZDOTDIR:-$HOME&#125;</span>/.zshrc</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> /usr/<span class="built_in">local</span>/share/zsh-syntax-highlighting/zsh-syntax-highlighting.zsh</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="设置主题"><a href="#设置主题" class="headerlink" title="设置主题"></a>设置主题</h2><p>使用主题 <a href="https://github.com/fcamblor/oh-my-zsh-agnoster-fcamblor" target="_blank" rel="external">agnoster</a>。   </p>
<h4 id="此款主题需要字体"><a href="#此款主题需要字体" class="headerlink" title="此款主题需要字体"></a>此款主题需要字体</h4><p><a href="https://github.com/powerline/fonts" target="_blank" rel="external">下载地址</a>  </p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment">#更改配置文件</span></div><div class="line">vi ~/.zshrc</div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#写入</span></div><div class="line">ZSH_THEME=<span class="string">"agnoster"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="成果"><a href="#成果" class="headerlink" title="成果"></a>成果</h2><p><img src="http://odai7z850.bkt.clouddn.com/zsh.png" alt="on-my-zsh"><br><img src="http://odai7z850.bkt.clouddn.com/zsh2.png" alt="on-my-zsh"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>参考：<br><a href="http://www.vpsee.com/2013/09/use-the-solarized-color-theme-on-mac-os-x-terminal/" target="_blank" rel="external">在 Mac OS X 终端里使用 Solarized 配色方案</a><br><a href="http://www.jianshu.com/p/7de00c73a2bb" target="_blank" rel="external">iTerm 2 &amp;&amp; Oh My Zsh【DIY教程——亲身体验过程】</a><br><a href="http://www.jianshu.com/p/e4973be9c9fb" target="_blank" rel="external">Mac下iTerm 2语法高亮配置及附带美化</a></p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;在MAC环境下自定义shell终端的配色方案。&lt;br&gt;iterm2 + oh my zsh&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
